metadata.name: Finito #1
metadata.description:
How many sat down, swayed, felt the freedom it must be to fly... With the wind hitting their face... The bravest with their hands loose and others hoping to get a complete turn.

Childhood passes, places stay. And there, reflections of people and moments where there is nothing else.
